author: CNET
description:
Innovative interactivity with custom game pieces makes this device more than just a fancy tablet with a gorgeous display. 

The Board comes with 12 pre-installed games with more coming soon, plus no subscription is needed. It's an immersive piece of equipment for people who value face-to-face time with friends and family. However, at $699, it's an investment for a console you can't use for other things like streaming and music. #board #boardgames #videogames #consoles #gaming #unboxing #tech #gaminggifts
